annotationA: Ubiquitin-like modifier-activating enzyme 5; E1-like enzyme which activates UFM1
annotationB: Ubiquitin conjugating enzyme 7, isoform A; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: defense response to Gram-negative bacterium; positive regulation of innate immune response; protein polyubiquitination; Belongs to the ubiquitin-conjugating enzyme family
